{"tid":674153,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"坤 哥 積 金 局 廣 告 全 年 最 高 收 看 率","createTime":"2018-05-22T12:38:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-27T16:05:49.000Z","uid":35964,"like":0,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f25a5c2f2d4ebecabd64dee6b63683636c486021","tid":674153,"uid":35964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T12:38:34.000Z","msg":"政府宣傳片一向都娘娘哋，不過舊年懶人基金推出時，積金局就特登搵坤哥拍廣告，重演「眼鏡起霧」嚟sell強積金，算係幾新鮮。<br />\n<br />\n原來呢條30秒嘅廣告片真係幾入屋，舊年係YouTube有成300萬hit rate，係全年最高收看率嘅廣告，幫積金局贏到個YouTube大獎。<br />\n<br />\n睇返前一年大獎得主萬寧貓，其實都係得160萬hit rate，今次積金局真係靠坤哥贏足一條街。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180517/large/b06_02_a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180517%2Flarge%2Fb06_02_a.jpg&h=f7d6e8a8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e792e1364c88ed80dc9662510207c2888167a204","tid":674153,"uid":135767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T12:50:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b229714ce88e431f7f5d34cc4b6195bc0d9e7277","tid":674153,"uid":121473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T15:16:27.000Z","msg":"坤gor<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b133b758b272f8df03cd1639453d6c40cb0e658","tid":674153,"uid":70391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T15:54:53.000Z","msg":"佢拍埋髮再生廣告 又搵袋幾十萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89a4fd7b37b134de66487ddd5de10b97ea5a0055","tid":674153,"uid":154684,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T16:04:48.000Z","msg":"冇睇過<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"466caceb7e75ee89c71b28b27bc706f88421d0e9","tid":674153,"uid":120908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"repl